===========================
🎓 Assignment: Movie Explorer App using TMDb API
===========================

📌 Objective:
-------------
Build a React application that mimics the "Upcoming Movies" page from the live project:
https://movie-exp-iota.vercel.app/movies/upcoming

Use the TMDb (The Movie Database) API to fetch and display movie data.

Live Reference Site: https://movie-exp-iota.vercel.app/movies/upcoming  
GitHub Repo: https://github.com/VyomThaker-2154/Movie-Exp

📦 Features to Implement:
--------------------------

1. Upcoming Movies Page
   - Route: `/movies/upcoming`
   - Fetch data from TMDb "Upcoming" API endpoint
   - Display movie:
     - Poster
     - Title
     - Release Date
     - Language
     - Vote Average
     - Overview (shortened to 3-4 lines)
   - Implement pagination or infinite scroll to load more movies

2. Responsive Grid UI
   - Movie cards in a grid format
   - Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop

3. (Optional Bonus) Search Bar
   - Input to search upcoming movies
   - Use TMDb `/search/movie` endpoint

4. Loading & Error States
   - Show loading spinner or skeleton during fetch
   - Show error message or "no results" message if needed

5. (Optional Bonus) Simple Navbar
   - Navigation between sections like Upcoming, Top Rated, etc.

🔧 Tech Stack:
---------------
- React (v18+)
- React Router
- Axios or native Fetch API
- Tailwind CSS or basic CSS/SCSS
- (Optional) React Infinite Scroll Component

🔐 TMDb API Key Setup:
-----------------------

1. Create a free account at: https://www.themoviedb.org
2. Go to: https://developer.themoviedb.org/
3. Generate a v3 API key (or v4 if preferred)
4. Add your key to a `.env` file in the root of your project:

   Example:
REACT_APP_TMDB_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

🌐 TMDb API Reference:
-----------------------
- Upcoming Movies Endpoint:
https://developer.themoviedb.org/reference/movie-upcoming-list

Example:

📁 Suggested Folder Structure:
------------------------------
src/
├── components/
│   └── MovieCard.jsx
├── pages/
│   └── UpcomingMovies.jsx
├── App.jsx
├── api.js
├── index.js

📝 Deliverables:
----------------
- Functional React app replicating the upcoming movies page
- Clean and responsive UI
- Pagination or infinite scrolling for results
- Hosted on GitHub or zip file submission

✅ Notes:
---------
- Match styling and features of: https://movie-exp-iota.vercel.app/movies/upcoming
- You may reuse styles from Tailwind or customize your own

Good luck and happy coding! 🎬🚀
